|Peter II&lt;br&gt;25 April 1196 – 13 September 1213||||1178&lt;br&gt;Huesca&lt;br&gt;son of Alfonso II and Sancha of Castile||Maria of Montpellier&lt;br&gt;15 June 1204 &lt;br&gt;2 children||12 September 1213&lt;br&gt;Battle of Muret&lt;br&gt;aged approximately 35
