|Ferdinand I the Honest&lt;br&gt;24 June 1412 – 2 April 1416||||27 November 1380&lt;br&gt;Medina del Campo&lt;br&gt;son of John I of Castile and Eleanor of Aragon||Eleanor of Alburquerque&lt;br&gt;1394&lt;br&gt;8 children||2 April 1416&lt;br&gt;Igualada&lt;br&gt;aged 36
