* Shigeru Egami &quot;The Heart of Karate-Do&quot; (Kodansha, 1976)
* Shiko Hokari &quot;Origins: A History of Shintaido&quot; (Shintaido of America, 1989)
* &quot;Cutting the Blue Sky&quot; by Shintaido of America

